Package uni.bielefeld.cmg.reflexiv.util

This package contains different classes for utilities such as option parsing and information displaying.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InfoManager
    This is an interface for managing program information.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultParam
    A data structure class that stores all default parameters.
    HelpParam
    Returns an object for dumping help information to the screen.
    InfoDumper
    Returns an object for printing messages in a structured format to the screen.
    InfoLogger
    Returns an object for logging messages in a structured format.
    Parameter
    Returns an object for parsing the input options for Reflexiv run.
    ParameterOfCounter
    Returns an object for parsing the input options for Reflexiv counter.
    ParameterOfReAssembler
    Returns an object for parsing the input options for Sparkhit-recruiter.
